trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged"></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: Tillhandahåller data för den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged"> </xref> händelse.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Den här klassen kan inte ärvas.

trans-unit.source: ComponentChangedEventArgs provides data for a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: ComponentChangedEventArgs tillhandahåller data för en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged>händelse.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged> event notifies the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService> and registered event handlers that a particular component in the currently active document has been changed.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged>händelse meddelar den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService>och registrerad händelsehanterare att en viss komponent i det aktiva dokumentet har ändrats.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged>

trans-unit.source: A ComponentChangedEventArgs provides the following information: - A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs.Component%2A> property that indicates the component that was modified.
trans-unit.target: En ComponentChangedEventArgs innehåller följande information: - A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs.Component%2A>egenskap som anger den komponent som har ändrats.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs.Component%2A>

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs.Member%2A> property that indicates the member that was changed.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs.Member%2A>egenskap som anger den medlem som har ändrats.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs.Member%2A>

trans-unit.source: - A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs.NewValue%2A> property that indicates the new value of the member.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs.NewValue%2A>egenskap som anger det nya värdet för medlemmen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs.NewValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: - An <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs.OldValue%2A> property that indicates the old value of the member.
trans-unit.target: -En <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs.OldValue%2A>egenskap som anger det gamla värdet för medlemmen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs.OldValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: Component designers typically raise the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged> event automatically when components are added, removed, or modified.
trans-unit.target: Komponenten designers ökar vanligtvis den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged>händelse automatiskt om komponenter som läggs till, tas bort eller ändras.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged> event is not raised during form load and unload because changes at this time are expected.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged>händelsen inte uppstår under formuläret belastning och ta bort eftersom ändringar i nuläget förväntas.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged>

trans-unit.source: A component designer might raise the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged> event after it changes a property of the component; this ensures that the Properties window will display the updated property.
trans-unit.target: En Komponentdesigner kan öka den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged>efter att det ändrar en egenskap för komponenten; Detta säkerställer att egenskapen uppdaterade visas i fönstret Egenskaper.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.IComponentChangeService.ComponentChanged>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentChangedEventArgs"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: The designer for a component calls this constructor after it has changed a property of the component.
trans-unit.target: Designer för en komponent anropar den här konstruktorn när en egenskap för komponenten har ändrats.

trans-unit.source: This ensures that the Properties window will display the property's updated value.
trans-unit.target: Detta säkerställer att den uppdaterade egenskapsvärde visas i fönstret Egenskaper.
